00:09:50,673 --> 00:09:51,758
<i>The church to Erin.</i>

76
00:09:52,717 --> 00:09:54,095
<i>The church to Father Paul.</i>

77
00:09:54,178 --> 00:09:56,012
<i>Bring in Erin. Scratch that. Try this.</i>

78
00:09:56,097 --> 00:09:58,182
<i>The rage bubbled up,
